 Jing Xi Chi, how about you? 

31
00:02:28,820 --> 00:02:31,160
 I'm the same as Cong. 

32
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:32,823
 What about your second choice? 

33
00:02:32,823 --> 00:02:34,238
 I didn't fill out a second choice. 

34
00:02:34,238 --> 00:02:37,160
 You didn't? How bold you are! 

35
00:02:37,160 --> 00:02:39,231
 What if you don't get in? 

36
00:02:39,231 --> 00:02:41,701
 What else? I'll just retake it. 

37
00:02:41,701 --> 00:02:43,500
 What are you talking about? 

38
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:46,510
 You know how hard this year has been. 

39
00:02:48,790 --> 00:02:50,240
What's wrong?

40
00:02:50,240 --> 00:02:51,412
Not happy?

41
00:02:51,412 --> 00:02:53,180
Do you think the stuff Dad bought is old-fashioned?

42
00:02:53,180 --> 00:02:54,400
He doesn't have an eye for fashion.

43
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:56,320
Doesn't look good? I can get you something else.

44
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:58,340
No, Dad.

45
00:02:59,990 --> 00:03:03,460
I just feel that... I'm going to university.

46
00:03:03,460 --> 00:03:11,540
Leaving home for another city, being away from friends and parents... I feel a bit reluctant.

47
00:03:11,540 --> 00:03:13,605
Tianhe isn't far from Wuan.

48
00:03:13,605 --> 00:03:15,397
That's less than an hour away by high-speed rail.

49
00:03:15,397 --> 00:03:18,000
- If you're homesick, come back every week. 
 - Yeah.

50
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:20,990
When I have time, I'll visit you whenever I can.

51
00:03:20,990 --> 00:03:23,560
Huan Er, your mom is right.

52
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,790
Just come back if you miss home.

53
00:03:24,790 --> 00:03:27,121
If it gets too hard, it's fine not to go to university.

54
00:03:27,121 --> 00:03:31,570
Dad! Can you wish me something good for once?

55
00:03:33,970 --> 00:03:35,200
Oh, yeah, Mom.

56
00:03:35,200 --> 00:03:38,850
Has Jing Xi Chi received his admission letter yet?

57
00:03:38,850 --> 00:03:41,250
- I don't know. 
 - I do.

58
00:03:41,250 --> 00:03:42,450
How do you know?

59
00:03:42,450 --> 00:03:46,640
I saw it. A delivery man went to their house a few days ago and delivered a letter.

60
